'''外耳'''（英文：Outer ear 或 external ear 或 auris externa），是[[耳|耳]]的外部结构，包括[[耳廓|耳廓]]和[[外耳道|外耳道]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=External Ear - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/external-ear|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315145541/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/external-ear|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Anatomy, Head and Neck, Ear|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK470359/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=29262017|first=Alice|last=Szymanski|first2=Zachary|last2=Geiger|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315145619/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK470359/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 外耳负责收集[[声能|声能]]，将其传递至[[中耳|中耳]]的[[鼓膜|鼓膜]]处<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=External ear {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/external-ear?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-07|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429095937/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/external-ear?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==

=== 耳廓 ===
[[耳廓|耳廓]]是外耳位于体外可见的部分，内部由一层黄色[[弹性软骨|弹性软骨]]组成<ref name=":0" />。耳廓与周围部位通过[[肌肉|肌肉]]和[[韧带|韧带]]相连，与外耳道口通过[[结缔组织|结缔组织]]相连<ref name=":0" />。许多[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]可以藉由移动耳廓以更好地接受不同方位的声音，但是[[人类|人类]]并不具有此项能力。人耳的耳廓底部有[[耳垂|耳垂]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ear Deformities|url=https://www.chop.edu/conditions-diseases/ear-deformities|accessdate=2021-03-07|date=2014-05-12|last=|first=|work=|publisher=The Children's Hospital of Philadelphia|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709161532/https://www.chop.edu/conditions-diseases/ear-deformities|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 外耳道 ===
耳廓收集的声波进入进入[[外耳道|外耳道]]，直通中耳的[[鼓膜|鼓膜]]处<ref name=":0" />。

== 临床 ==
外耳畸形可由[[遗传疾病|遗传疾病]]导致，也可由如[[辐射|辐射]]、[[感染|感染]]之类的环境因素导致，包括[[耳前瘻管|耳前瘘管]]、[[克魯松氏症候群|克鲁松氏症候群]]等。许多可通过手术矫正<ref>{{Cite web|title=耳道闭锁和小耳畸形|url=https://www.hear-it.org/cn/hear/article/102580|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=www.hear-it.org|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927130442/https://www.hear-it.org/cn/hear/article/102580|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Congenital Deformities of the Outer Ear|url=https://www.yalemedicine.org/conditions/congenital-deformities-of-the-outer-ear|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=Yale Medicine|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526222418/https://www.yalemedicine.org/conditions/congenital-deformities-of-the-outer-ear|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此外，[[细菌|细菌]]等感染可以发[[外耳炎|外耳炎]]，俗称“游泳耳”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Swimmer's ear - Symptoms and causes|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/swimmers-ear/symptoms-causes/syc-20351682|accessdate=2021-03-07|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503135127/https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/swimmers-ear/symptoms-causes/syc-20351682|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

